Install Docker:

  sudo apt-get docker docker.io


Get the sqlillo dependencies

  sudo docker pull tarasyarema/sqlillo


Outside the files folder, execute a simulation, and generates a .json file, you can enter it into the game website:

  sudo docker run -v "$(pwd)/files":/files --rm -it tarasyarema/sqlillo files/<<filename>>.lua files/>>filename>>.lua
  
  
Update docker image:

  sudo docker pull tarasyarema/sqlillo



